  Mercury_Aries: `Solar return Mercury in Aries brings speed, directness, and competitive intellectual energy to the year's mental style and communicative approach. The mind operates quickly and decisively, and the year tends to reward those who trust their rapid conclusions and act on them without excessive second-guessing. The characteristic risk is that of premature judgment or the assumption that speed equals accuracy — the year favours those who use Mercury's natural quickness as a bridge to genuine understanding rather than those for whom the first impulse becomes the final word.`,

